## ğŸš€ Features

- âœ”ï¸ Download files from a TFTP server (**GET**)
- âœ”ï¸ Upload files to a TFTP server (**PUT**)
- âœ”ï¸ Supports **octet** (binary) transfer mode
- âœ”ï¸ Handles **error codes** and retransmissions
- âœ”ï¸ Timeout handling for unreliable networks
- âœ”ï¸ Uses **structured packet processing** (RFC 1350)

